 />\n唔好咁低能啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:24:21.000Z","msg":"終國做其他事會柒<br />\n但封呢樣個樣最撚叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:26:11.000Z","msg":"根本應該改做內聯網同北韓一樣"},{"pid":"3adb070b154ab13ceec0cd86b0fe661788ba5549","tid":845046,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:27:10.000Z","msg":"自己贏到開巷，要被對手小小甜頭<br />\n<br />\n以德報怨呀，高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05aeddc1d930ed75b95129e83efd0bad8e39bb0f","tid":845046,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6a19352374710ee8cb72642d3ebd4171bff5fd3","tid":845046,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:21:43.000Z","msg":"而家上網咁方便，點封都無用<br />\n唔好咁低能啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:27:46.000Z","msg":"之前有調查<br />\n全中國13億人<br />\n但網民只有5億幾人左右 (主要都是大城市)<br />\n<br />\n即係話, 仲有至少7億人, 係唔識上網 , 主要都是內陸窮人<br />\n佢地平時係透過CCTV 了解時事<br />\n<br />\n另外,5億網民 入面, 好多上網都係為左玩樂, 佢地睇新聞多數都係睇 QQ, 新浪果D就算, 唔會再去了解真相<br />\n<br />\n所以封鎖消息, 絕對有效的"},{"pid":"93b7c50ddba7a2266ad69ab15d9021b283c33142","tid":845046,"uid":55913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:41:21.000Z","msg":"支那點會有壞既事<br />\n隔離po先有人讚自由自在<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7df3e03b16cf7c2643f4440762fc832772513e9","tid":845046,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:44:34.000Z","msg":"大獲全勝"},{"pid":"33053449b98445fae8cb75a7b7ee8c9123562a3a","tid":845046,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93b7c50ddba7a2266ad69ab15d9021b283c33142","tid":845046,"uid":55913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:41:21.000Z","msg":"支那點會有壞既事<br />\n隔離po先有人讚自由自在<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class